snippet.title: FRAMED 2 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
FRAMED 2 is a noir puzzle game where you re-arrange panels of a comic book to solve a series of imaginative puzzles, and change the outcome of the story.

Set years before the original, FRAMED 2 is the follow up to Hideo Kojima's 2014 Game Of The Year, FRAMED.

FRAMED 1: 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/framed/id886565180?mt=8
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.noodlecake.framed

Facebook: http://facebook.com/LoveshackEntertainment.
